      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Pham Hong Nguyen</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:P0.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2c/P0.jpg/300px-P0.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"266\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2c/P0.jpg/450px-P0.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2c/P0.jpg/600px-P0.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:P0.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Nguyen Pham</div></div></div> \n<p><b>Pham Hong Nguyen</b>, (given name is Nguyen) <br />\na Vietnamese scientist working on <a href=\"/Artificial_Intelligence\" title=\"Artificial Intelligence\">AI</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Natural_language_processing\">NLP</a> compiler fields. Chess programming is his main hobby. He has developed some programs for both <a href=\"/Chess\" title=\"Chess\">chess</a> and <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a> (Xiangqi). He is author of the <a href=\"/Banksia\" title=\"Banksia\">Banksia</a> <a href=\"/CLI\" title=\"CLI\">CLI</a> <a href=\"/Tournament_Manager\" title=\"Tournament Manager\">Tournament Manager</a>, and the <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">Graphical User Interface</a> <a href=\"/Banksia_GUI\" title=\"Banksia GUI\">Banksia GUI</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Chess\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Chinese_Chess_.28Xiangqi.29\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chinese Chess (Xiangqi)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2002\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2002</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess\">Chess</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pham_Hong_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Chess\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ax\" title=\"Ax\">Ax</a>: A so-so chess engine </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/FirstChess\" title=\"FirstChess\">FirstChess</a>: a very simple chess (open source code) to help newbies to learn chess programming</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Banksia\" title=\"Banksia\">Banksia</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Banksia_GUI\" title=\"Banksia GUI\">Banksia GUI</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chinese_Chess_.28Xiangqi.29\">Chinese Chess (Xiangqi)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pham_Hong_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Chinese Chess (Xiangqi)\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=VSCCP&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"VSCCP (page does not exist)\">VSCCP</a> (Very Simple Chinese Chess Program): the first World open-source code for Chinese Chess <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> CCW (Chinese Chess World): a combination of chess program and chess book viewer </li>\n<li> CCC (Coffee Chinese Chess): a Java applet to play or view chess games </li>\n<li> XB (Xiangqi database browser): view chess game database </li>\n<li> Saola - The Chinese chess challenger: a very strong chess engine - grandmaster level</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Publications\">Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pham_Hong_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Hong Pham</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>A completed implementation for Xiangqi rules</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#40_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 40, No. 3</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Hong Pham</a> (<b>2024</b>). <i>Chinese Chess EGTB with Perpetual Check-Chase Rules</i>. CG-2024</li></ul>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pham_Hong_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2002\">2002</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pham_Hong_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2002\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=37429\">Ax - a new engine from a newbie</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pham Hong Nguyen</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">WinBoard Forum</a>, May 24, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Ax\" title=\"Ax\">Ax</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=242289\">FirstChess - a crazy project!</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pham Hong Nguyen</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/FirstChess\" title=\"FirstChess\">FirstChess</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pham_Hong_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64030\">Probe EGT in quiescence?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 20, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Xiangqi</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66337\">A new design for Xianqgi (Chinese chess) Endgame Tablebase</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 16, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69386\">A proposal for Jeiqi notation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 26, 2018  </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69447\">Generate EGTB with graphics cards?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 01, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=71157&amp;hilit=banksia\">Banksia - Yet another Chess Tournament Manager</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 01, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Banksia\" title=\"Banksia\">Banksia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=72019&amp;start=36\">Re: PGN standard, its improvement and standardization</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 14, 2019&#160;» from <a href=\"/Portable_Game_Notation\" title=\"Portable Game Notation\">Portable Game Notation</a> to <a href=\"/Protocols\" title=\"Protocols\">Protocols</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=72350\">Banksia GUI released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Banksia_GUI\" title=\"Banksia GUI\">Banksia GUI</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pham_Hong_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=78464\">Open Chess Game Database Standard (OCGDB)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 20, 2021&#160;» <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">Chess Databases</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://talkchess.com/viewtopic.php?t=83676\">Felicity EGTB generators and probers</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Nguyen Pham</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 20, 2024&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pham_Hong_Nguyen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://xiang-qi.appspot.com/software.html\">Chinese Chess (Xiang Qi) Software 1</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228200824\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.014 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.017 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 49/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 86/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4981-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228200824 and revision id 27284\n -->\n"
